            <div class=3D"calculator-container">
                <p><strong>Euler Totient Function Calculator</strong> compu=
tes =CF=86(n), which counts the positive integers up to n that are relative=
ly prime to n. This function is fundamental in number theory and cryptograp=
hy.</p>
               =20
                <div class=3D"section">
                    <h3>Input</h3>
                    <div class=3D"input-row">
                        <div class=3D"input-group">
                            <label for=3D"numberInput">Enter a positive int=
eger (n)</label>
